## Example application properties for MS-Profile (DO NOT COMMIT real secrets)

spring.application.name=MS_PROFILE
server.port=8086

spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/profile_ms_db?createDatabaseIfNotExist=true
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=${MYSQL_PASSWORD:change_me}

## NVIDIA API key (set in environment)
app.nvidia.api-key=${NVIDIA_NIM_API_KEY:}
